Version 0.4.0 (2022-04-27)
--------------------------
Add back-off on 100% event sending failure (#9)
Add event-level Subject (#61)
Add IP address property to Subject (#62)
Rename send_limit to batch_size in Emitter (#63)

Version 0.3.0 (2022-04-19)
--------------------------
Add support for Linux in HTTP client (#5)
Add CI build on Linux and update build instructions (#50)
Add support for Linux in desktop context (#47)
Add support for Linux when generating UUIDs (#46)
Use a common Event base class for all event types (#51)
Add emitter callback function (#7)
Add customizable no-retry HTTP status codes (#54)
Expose an interface for storage and make it configurable (#48)
Add a header file that includes all the published APIs (#55)

Version 0.2.0 (2022-02-24)
--------------------------
Update session when events are tracked (#35)
Allow custom User Agent strings (#23)
Use snowplow namespace (#13)
Add support for C++17 (#36)
Update sqlite3 to latest version due to use of deprecated APIs (#24)
Add API documentation (#40)
Update copyright notices (#26)
Fix links to documentation in README (#25)
Build and release using Github actions (#27)
Add performance testing setup (#37)
Follow a code style guide (#44)
Change all OS-X references to macOS (#11)

